          "ability_type": "offensive",
          "activation_name": "Embed Location",
          "activation_time": "10 minutes",
          "effect": "By focusing on the *Guiding Star Orb*, you embed your current location in the item. Thereafter, anyone who holds the *Guiding Star Orb* while Casting a Spell with the teleportation trait to travel to this location arrives precisely, without any inaccuracy at all. The *Guiding Star Orb* can only have one location embedded at a time; if you use this activity a second time, the new location replaces the previous one.",
