        {
          "ability_type": "offensive",
          "activation_name": "Momentary Aiudara",
          "activation_time": "10 minutes",
          "effect": "You cause a shimmering magical archway to appear next to you as the *Guiding Star Orb* casts a 7th-rank *teleport* to your specifications. If you are teleporting to an aiudara you\u2019ve visited before, you and the targets appear precisely at that location.",
